magicbook.gtlitecore.api.module

注释类型 Module


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Module

    • 必需元素概要

      所需元素 
      限定符和类型 必需的元素和说明
      java.lang.String containerId
      Id of the container (ModuleContainer) to associate the module with.
      java.lang.String moduleId
      Id of the module, must be unique within its container (containerId).
      java.lang.String name
      Name of the module, used human-readable name.

    • 可选元素概要

      可选元素 
      限定符和类型 可选元素和说明
      java.lang.String author
      Author of the module.
      java.lang.String descriptions
      A description of the module in the module configuration file.
      boolean isCore
      Whether the module is the core module for its container.
      java.lang.String[] modDependencies
      A list of ModIds that the module depends on.
      java.lang.String version
      Version of the module.

    • 元素详细资料

      • moduleId

        public abstract java.lang.String moduleId
        Id of the module, must be unique within its container (containerId).

      • containerId

        public abstract java.lang.String containerId
        Id of the container (ModuleContainer) to associate the module with.

      • name

        public abstract java.lang.String name
        Name of the module, used human-readable name.

      • modDependencies

        public abstract java.lang.String[] modDependencies
        A list of ModIds that the module depends on. If any mods specified are not present, the module will not load.
        默认值:
        {}

      • isCore

        public abstract boolean isCore
        Whether the module is the core module for its container. Each container must have exactly one core module which will be loaded before all other modules in the container. Core modules should not have mod dependencies because this module used to loaded mod structure from API to mod main.
        默认值:
        false

      • author

        public abstract java.lang.String author
        Author of the module.
        默认值:
        ""

      • version

        public abstract java.lang.String version
        Version of the module.
        默认值:
        ""

      • descriptions

        public abstract java.lang.String descriptions
        A description of the module in the module configuration file.
        默认值:
        ""
